# Placeholder — Figma export targets

Export the following frames from `image-scale-modes.fig` (one SVG per
frame, using the frame name as the file name):

  - scale-stretch.svg
  - scale-fit.svg
  - scale-fill.svg
  - scale-tile.svg

Once the SVGs land here, this `.gitkeep` can stay or be removed —
git keeps the directory either way.
